Jack Soo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Soo 0 Jack Soo (October 28, 1917 – January 11, 1979) was a Japanese American actor. He was best known for his role as Detective Nick Yemana on the television sitcom Barney Miller. Jack_Soo ( October_28_,_1917 – January_11_,_1979 ) was a_Japanese_American_actor .
